name: v0.1
body:
Sous version 0.1 makes a number of changes, some of which may be backwards-incompatible.

Please see the [release notes](https://github.com/opentable/sous/blob/master/doc/sous0.1.md) for full details of the changes, and how they may impact your workflow.

It is recommended that all users of Sous upgrade to this latest version.

Very short summary:
- A number of new features for the CLI:
  - sous deploy command (alpha)
  - -flavor flag, and support for flavours
  - -source flag which can be used instead of -repo and -offset
- Automatic migrations for the Docker image name cache
- Consistent identifier parse and print round-tripping
- Updates to various pieces of documentation
- Nicer Singularity request names
